? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebc27faffa4c66ed18911bdc3afc5a1862d1027","tid":372340,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵下炒散先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想無咁頹，但唔想返炒散，我要長工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有介紹? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返住保安先，訓教都有錢收"},{"pid":"dd025abbfda9ecf98e1110f6e19b611b6812295c","tid":372340,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"有咩要求？"},{"pid":"d53353a7f8ad4eb0424ee3a9dc99e1a2d0a542e0","tid":372340,"uid":57796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"得我一個無工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15242bdddc350582a608718c8ddb5813ccc2b80d","tid":372340,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9271a2b8a6a168067521f107ecb613d16fe76e","tid":372340,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"唔洗做 不憂衣食 好爽"},{"pid":"f4b8bf1937b52722e51f9000af6e8ab7671486bc","tid":372340,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"30dba29aaf66e7b425d948e39498ca40874e18ba","tid":372340,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"好想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae197def6c81f45e6a7b1beb4c138a9823b34332","tid":372340,"uid":133514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:04:24.000